{"vv4:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv4:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv4:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv4:0.4":"4. Catutthapithavimanavatthu ","vv4:1.1":"“Pitham te veluriyamayam ularam, ","vv4:1.2":"Manojavam gacchati yenakamam; ","vv4:1.3":"Alankate malyadhare suvatthe, ","vv4:1.4":"Obhasasi vijjurivabbhakutam. ","vv4:2.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv4:2.2":"kena te idha mijjhati; ","vv4:2.3":"Uppajjanti ca te bhoga, ","vv4:2.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv4:3.1":"Pucchami tam devi mahanubhave, ","vv4:3.2":"Manussabhuta kimakasi punnam; ","vv4:3.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv4:3.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv4:4.1":"Sa devata attamana, ","vv4:4.2":"moggallanena pucchita; ","vv4:4.3":"Panham puttha viyakasi, ","vv4:4.4":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv4:5.1":"“Appassa kammassa phalam mamedam, ","vv4:5.2":"Yenamhi evam jalitanubhava; ","vv4:5.3":"Aham manussesu manussabhuta, ","vv4:5.4":"Purimaya jatiya manussaloke. ","vv4:6.1":"Addasam virajam bhikkhum, ","vv4:6.2":"vippasannamanavilam; ","vv4:6.3":"Tassa adasaham pitham, ","vv4:6.4":"pasanna sehi panibhi. ","vv4:7.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv4:7.2":"tena me idha mijjhati; ","vv4:7.3":"Uppajjanti ca me bhoga, ","vv4:7.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv4:8.1":"Akkhami te bhikkhu mahanubhava, ","vv4:8.2":"Manussabhuta yamakasi punnam; ","vv4:8.3":"Tenamhi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv4:8.4":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv4:9.1":"Catutthapithavimanam catuttham. "}